OL,3,CPoliticians remember former UTV
OL,4,CPolitical Editor Ken Reid at Stormont
OL,6,FAt Stormont on Monday, representatives
OL,7,Ffrom across the political spectrum
OL,8,Fpraised his professionalism,
OL,9,Fimpartiality and personality.
OL,11,FMatthew O'Toole from the SDLP, said:
OL,12,F"Conversations with him were always
OL,13,Flife-enhancing. You could start about
OL,14,Fsome controversial issue of the day
OL,15,Fand then very quickly find yourself
OL,16,Forganically getting onto football or
OL,17,Fmusic."
