OL,3,CPoliticians remember former UTV
OL,4,CPolitical Editor Ken Reid at Stormont
OL,6,FThe Speaker of the Assembly, Edwin
OL,7,FPoots, knew Ken for years, and said:
OL,8,F"Ken and I disagreed on many things;
OL,9,FLinfield, Cliftonville, Liverpool,
OL,10,FEverton, Van Morrison, Phil Collins.
OL,11,FHis music taste was terrible, his
OL,12,Ffootball taste was terrible, but
OL,13,Fnonetheless he was a really fine
OL,14,Fjournalist and he was a really fine
OL,15,Fgentleman."
OL,17,FA heartfelt tribute was also made by
OL,18,Fthe Health Minister, Mike Nesbitt, who
OL,19,Fhad worked with Ken for many years at
OL,20,FUTV.
