OL,3,CPoliticians remember former UTV
OL,4,CPolitical Editor Ken Reid at Stormont
OL,6,FHe said: "He was, frankly, for all
OL,7,Fthat time my broadcasting brother and
OL,8,FI am so grateful to have had that
OL,9,Fopportunity."
OL,11,FKen's funeral will take place in his
OL,12,Fadopted home town of Ballymena on
OL,13,FThursday 28 November.
